----------------------------------------------------------------------
HelloMavens editorial enrichments and overrides
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The following files are HelloMavens-authored editorial work, layered on
top of the SBS standard. They are NOT derived from SBS and are MIT-
licensed (not CC BY-SA):

  packages/sbs-engine/data/control-enrichments.json
  packages/sbs-engine/data/control-enrichments.RATIONALE.md
  packages/sbs-engine/data/control-overrides.json
  packages/sbs-engine/data/control-overrides.LICENSE.txt

control-enrichments.json maps each control to OWASP Top 10 2021 and
regulatory citations (HIPAA Security Rule, SOC 2 TSC 2017, ISO
27001:2022 Annex A, GDPR, CCPA), sourced from the authoritative
publications cited in the file's `sources` field.

control-overrides.json holds risk-level overrides for controls whose
upstream YAML is missing a required field. Currently overrides
SBS-AUTH-004 (upstream omits risk_level; we pin to Critical based on
the control's narrative).
